Detailed Description

cvmx_pko_mem_port_rate1

Notes: Writing PKO_MEM_PORT_RATE1[PID,RATE_LIM] has the side effect of setting the corresponding accumulator to zero. This CSR is a memory of 44 entries, and thus, the PKO_REG_READ_IDX CSR must be written before any CSR read operations to this address can be performed. A read of any entry that has not been previously written is illegal and will result in unpredictable CSR read data.
